snippet.title: The Sims 2 Mobile (2005, Java) | gameplay, no commentary
snippet.description:
First 20 minutes of The Sims 2 Mobile gameplay (unconnected edition for high-end phones). The Sims 2 was released in 2005 for mobile phones capable of running Java applications such as Nokia 6600.
You can read more about the game here https://sims.fandom.com/wiki/The_Sims_2_(mobile). You can watch gameplay of the low-end version here https://youtu.be/X95aA6SgtSQ

Please be aware that the game features no music and only a handful of sound effects that might be too loud unless you adjust your volume beforehand.
